## Browser And Device Support

To illustrate our browser support requirements, we're borrowing this nifty table from [Bootstrap's browser support section](http://getbootstrap.com/getting-started/#support).

![Browser Support Requirements Table](/images/browser-support.png)

This means that templates must support the latest stable version of each listed browser on each platform where the two intersect with a checkmark. **For Internet Explorer, we require support of IE10+.**

**We do not require support of IE9, IE8, IE7, or IE6**, but you will have to specify whether your template supports these browsers, so you may want to consider doing so if gaining a somewhat wider market is worth the extra the effort.

We do not require support for any additional browsers or devices.

